Kenyan comedian Vincent Muasya aka Chipukeezy on Tuesday shared a photo of his meeting with US comedian Kevin Hart.Chipukeezy, who is in the US for a series of standup shows, said he received great encouragement on his comedy career from&nbsp;Hart in their meeting.Hart was in Los Angeles on a tour to promote his book tour&nbsp;new book, " I Can&rsquo;t Make This Up: Life Lessons."Chipukeezy said the encounter was a dream come true tar and was honoured that Hart shared encouraging words.